，包含3大核心部分\n- ✅ 内容详实，可直接应用于团队管理\n- ✅ 配套完善，包含表单模板、制度文件参考\n- ✅ 版本管理规范，含修订记录\n\n### 🚫 阻塞项\n无阻塞项，任务已完成。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai_libu_hr","model":"glm-4.7","usage":{"input":4367,"output":1387,"cacheRead":12850,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":18604,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773879003699}}
